SuperSwifty2004's Water Powered Engines Mod

This mod adds water propelled engines and generators.

Adds:

  • WPR-1 Engine
  • WPR-5 Engine
  • Bottle o' Karbonated Water
  • XXXXXL Karbonated Water Can

Installation

Unzip Files into GameData

Attributions:

  • Community Resource Pack (RoverDude)
  • Zzz (models for generators)

Download: http://www.curse.com/ksp-mods/kerbal/228316-superswifty2004s-water-powered-engine-mod

Edited March 16, 2015 by SuperSwifty2004

Welcome aboard SuperSwifty2004!

There is no download link in your OP, and before adding one I must ask that your review our Add-On Posting Rules, in particular the part about including a license for your work in both the download itself and the OP.
Also its not a rule but a "rule" the community follows and that is we need some pictures of your work! Welcome to the forums and can't wait to see what you got in store!
